*Linux-Pid-0.40.0-r1 (22 Aug 2014)

  22 Aug 2014; Ian Stakenvicius (_AxS_) <axs@gentoo.org>
  +Linux-Pid-0.40.0-r1.ebuild, -Linux-Pid-0.40.0.ebuild:
  bumped EAPI to 5; committed directly to stable as no other changes present and
  revbump helps stable systems to keep from dieing on perl-5.18 upgrade

  13 Nov 2012; Brent Baude <ranger@gentoo.org> Linux-Pid-0.40.0.ebuild:
  Marking Linux-Pid-0.40.0 ppc64 for bug 432610

  10 Oct 2012; Brent Baude <ranger@gentoo.org> Linux-Pid-0.40.0.ebuild:
  Marking Linux-Pid-0.40.0 ppc for bug 432610

  18 Sep 2012; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> Linux-Pid-0.40.0.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #432610).

